Colouring Circuit Breaker (CCB) 🤣 Besides colouring mandalas my latest craze is unique head shot of women especially those with long hair & fancy clothes. My fave is Pic 1. That’s the one I finished a few minutes ago. I love it because it says My Style 🤣Pretty much my style 🥰 This is one of the ways I spend my time now 🤩🌟✨💫⭐️ #joyinenjoy #stayhomeSG
Thanks my dear @ztudioasia for the compliments 😍🙌
This is soooo creative and out of the box 💓💓 wonderful 🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻
Tht’s so beautiful 😍 Will you point me where I can try my hands on colouring too?
